    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and minor curb rash on the wheels. Inside, the upholstery shows some thinning and a few small stains, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully functional. Mechanically, it starts consistently and runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It is an honest, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 21000.0,
